# Checking multiple logs.
> init
<<<
+ zerot.txt zerot.txt
> add zerot.txt
<<<
> commit "just added zerot"
<<<
+ zulu.txt test3.txt
> add zulu.txt
<<< 
> commit "Zulu added"
<<< 
> status 
=== Branches ===
*master

=== Staged Files ===

=== Removed Files ===

=== Modifications Not Staged For Commit ===

=== Untracked Files ===

<<<
+ zama.txt test1.txt
> add zama.txt
<<<
> status
=== Branches ===
*master

=== Staged Files ===
zama.txt

=== Removed Files ===

=== Modifications Not Staged For Commit ===

=== Untracked Files ===

<<<
> commit "adding zama"
<<<
D peep "commit [a-f0-9]+"
D zoot "Date: \w\w\w \w\w\w \d+ \d\d:\d\d:\d\d \d\d\d\d [-+]\d\d\d\d"
> log
===
${peep}
${zoot}
adding zama

